    <title></title>
    <link href="/2022/09/29/Linux/"/>
    <url>/2022/09/29/Linux/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<hr><h2 id="Linux笔记"><a href="#Linux笔记" class="headerlink" title="Linux笔记"></a>Linux笔记</h2><h1 id="Linux设置环境变量"><a href="#Linux设置环境变量" class="headerlink" title="Linux设置环境变量"></a>Linux设置环境变量</h1><h3 id="设置完成使用该命令刷新"><a href="#设置完成使用该命令刷新" class="headerlink" title="设置完成使用该命令刷新"></a><em><strong>设置完成使用该命令刷新</strong></em></h3><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs sh"><span class="hljs-built_in">source</span> 编辑的文件<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="临时设置"><a href="#临时设置" class="headerlink" title="临时设置"></a>临时设置</h3><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs sh"><span class="hljs-built_in">export</span> PATH=/you/bin/path:<span class="hljs-variable">$PATH</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="当前用户永久生效"><a href="#当前用户永久生效" class="headerlink" title="当前用户永久生效"></a>当前用户永久生效</h3><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs sh">vim ~/.bashrc<br><span class="hljs-built_in">export</span> PATH=/you/bin/path:<span class="hljs-variable">$PATH</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="所有用户永久生效（需要重新登录）"><a href="#所有用户永久生效（需要重新登录）" class="headerlink" title="所有用户永久生效（需要重新登录）"></a>所有用户永久生效<strong>（需要重新登录）</strong></h3><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs sh">//三者挑其一<br>vim /etc/bashrc<br>vim /etc/profile<br>vim /etc/environment<br>//添加下面的设置<br><span class="hljs-built_in">export</span> PATH=/you/bin/path:<span class="hljs-variable">$PATH</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="Java环境变量设置"><a href="#Java环境变量设置" class="headerlink" title="Java环境变量设置"></a>Java环境变量设置</h3><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs sh"><span class="hljs-built_in">export</span> JAVA_HOME=/usr/share/jdk1.6.0_14<br><span class="hljs-built_in">export</span> PATH=<span class="hljs-variable">$JAVA_HOME</span>/bin:<span class="hljs-variable">$PATH</span><br><span class="hljs-built_in">export</span> CLASSPATH=.:<span class="hljs-variable">$JAVA_HOME</span>/lib/dt.jar:<span class="hljs-variable">$JAVA_HOME</span>/lib/tools.jar<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="问题：安全检查"><a href="#问题：安全检查" class="headerlink" title="问题：安全检查"></a>问题：安全检查</h1><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs sh">fatal: detected dubious ownership <span class="hljs-keyword">in</span> repository at <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;/media/data/users/jhu3szh/serialize&#x27;</span><br>To add an exception <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> this directory, call:<br>git config --global --add safe.directory /media/data/users/jhu3szh/serialize<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="解决办法"><a href="#解决办法" class="headerlink" title="解决办法"></a>解决办法</h3><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs sh">//修改拥有者<br><span class="hljs-built_in">chown</span> -R user:user <span class="hljs-built_in">dir</span><br>//无效再使用一下方式<br>git config --global --add safe.directory <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;*&#x27;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="文件压缩、解压"><a href="#文件压缩、解压" class="headerlink" title="文件压缩、解压"></a>文件压缩、解压</h1><h3 id="tar解压"><a href="#tar解压" class="headerlink" title="tar解压"></a><strong>tar</strong>解压</h3><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs sh">tar -xvf 文件名<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="tar压缩"><a href="#tar压缩" class="headerlink" title="tar压缩"></a><strong>tar</strong>压缩</h3><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs sh">tar -cvf 压缩名称.tar 文件（目录）<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="用户创建"><a href="#用户创建" class="headerlink" title="用户创建"></a>用户创建</h1><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs sh">//创建用户<br>useradd uesrname<br><br>//创建用户和生成用户文件夹及shell<br>useradd username -m -s /bin/bash<br><br>//设置用户密码<br>passwd username<br><br>//允许用户使用sudo<br>usermod -a -G sudo username<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="SSH远程连接"><a href="#SSH远程连接" class="headerlink" title="SSH远程连接"></a>SSH远程连接</h1><h3 id="ssh：连接远程服务器"><a href="#ssh：连接远程服务器" class="headerlink" title="ssh：连接远程服务器"></a><strong>ssh</strong>：连接远程服务器</h3><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs sh">ssh username@ip<br>//如下<br>ssh root@www.test.com<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="scp：远程拷贝文件（ssh方式）"><a href="#scp：远程拷贝文件（ssh方式）" class="headerlink" title="scp：远程拷贝文件（ssh方式）"></a><strong>scp</strong>：远程拷贝文件（ssh方式）</h3><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs sh">scp filepath username@ip:targetPath<br>//如下<br>scp test.js root@www.test.com:/home/root<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="问题：Snap商店安装错误"><a href="#问题：Snap商店安装错误" class="headerlink" title="问题：Snap商店安装错误"></a>问题：Snap商店安装错误</h1><h3 id="问题描述："><a href="#问题描述：" class="headerlink" title="问题描述："></a>问题描述：</h3><p><strong>snap “xxxx” has “install-snap” change in progress</strong></p><h3 id="解决方法："><a href="#解决方法：" class="headerlink" title="解决方法："></a>解决方法：</h3><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs sh">//查看snap 正在安装的软件，获取<span class="hljs-built_in">id</span><br>snap changes<br><br>//终止安装软件<br>sudo snap abort <span class="hljs-built_in">id</span><br><br>//重新安装软件即可<br>sudo snap install xxx<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="Cat日志查看"><a href="#Cat日志查看" class="headerlink" title="Cat日志查看"></a>Cat日志查看</h1><p><strong>cat常用于查看指定日志信息，系统在运行时，日志会不断写入，如果使用vim等编辑器指令查看会无法得到全部的日志，同时也可能导致日志的修改。</strong></p><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs sh">//查看文件的全部内容<br><span class="hljs-built_in">cat</span> 文件名 <br>//如：<span class="hljs-built_in">cat</span> test.js<br><br>//对所有行添加编号输出，1开始<br><span class="hljs-built_in">cat</span> -n 文件名<br>//如：<span class="hljs-built_in">cat</span> -n test.js<br><br>//排除空白行添加编号输出<br><span class="hljs-built_in">cat</span> -b 文件名<br>//如：<span class="hljs-built_in">cat</span> -b test.js<br><br>//替换连续两行以上的空白行为一行空白行<br><span class="hljs-built_in">cat</span> -s 文件名<br>//如：<span class="hljs-built_in">cat</span> -b test.js<br><br>//结合grep查看指定内容<br><span class="hljs-built_in">cat</span> 文件名 | grep 搜索内容<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="Grep查看符合条件的内容"><a href="#Grep查看符合条件的内容" class="headerlink" title="Grep查看符合条件的内容"></a>Grep查看符合条件的内容</h1><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs sh">grep 查找内容 文件名<br>//如：grep hello test.js<br><br>//忽略大小写<br>grep -i 查找内容 文件名<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="Find查找文件位置"><a href="#Find查找文件位置" class="headerlink" title="Find查找文件位置"></a>Find查找文件位置</h1><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs sh">find 路径 &lt;选项&gt; 参数<br><br>//查找当前目录及子目录test.js<br>find . -name test.js<br><br>//查找所有目录test.js<br>find / -name test.js<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
    
